<br>
Some of the best times of all though is when I get to help someone out of a helpless situation. We lose sight of it sometimes with all the math and comparisons and so forth, but we really are an amazing class. There's nothing like going to Kelethin and filling the zone with floating wolves (Lev, share wolfie), and I still am thankful for the ability to port all over the world in the blink of an eye. I still get a kick out of saying &quot;BRT&quot; to someone on the other side of Norath...<br>
<br>
