<br>
Luckily, a call to arms rang out across the land, and a solid group of lvl 60's showed up.  Every one of them had thier epics and were decked out in the best possible gear for the time.  It was a sight to behold!  They fought all the way up to the 4th floor and rezzed my entire group, then evaced out before we could utter a thank you.<br>
<br>
It was the first time Ubers had ever been nice to me, much less took the time out of thier scheduale to help me.  Seeing all 6 of them with all that power was awsome.<br>
